          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Public Service Expansion Act</b></p> <p>This bill revises the definition of a public service job to include working at any nonprofit organization, regardless of the organization's mission, for the purposes of student loan repayment and public service student loan forgiveness.</p>]]></text>
